<li><a href="/wiki/Norman_Geisler" title="Norman Geisler">Geisler, Norman</a> and Thomas Howe, <i>When Critics Ask: A Popular Handbook on Bible Difficulties</i>; Baker Books, Grand Rapids Michigan; 1992.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Norman_Geisler" title="Norman Geisler">Geisler, Norman</a> (ed.), <i>Inerrancy</i>; <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0310392810" class="internal">ISBN 0-310-39281-0</a>; 1980.</li>
